Metadata: University of California Sea Grant/San Diego County Cooperative Extension

Tidelines will be published quarterly as a local newsletter dealing with practical problems in the areas of Commercial and sport fisheries; Seafood processing, aquaculture, marine education and youth programs, marine research, waterfront management, boating industry, marine transportation, environmental policy, and coastal engineering. Cover articles include: What if the sun were dangerous? Ozone and you - what to do? Getting to the Nonpoint of Pollution. NPS(nonpoint source pollution) Pilot Project.
